reviews.review_text: sugar mag>caution is amazing the transition is amazing with bill and phil just rockin it out!

heaven 72 so loose, like breathing without taking a breath.
we can share this show and the wine.

Settle down easy... Hey I thinks Weir sings a verse from the Frozen Logger just before El Paso.
If a wrote a song by song review of this show it would be as long and tripped as some of the papers I wrote in grad school.
Wow. Pigpen chooses some really sweet tunes during this show!
Lately it occurs to me...
WALSTIB
